name: to summon a god
description:
purple is the color that reminds me of you. the color that we share, the color of love and belonging, the color the belongs to our lover. 

i never used to think that i would share him, that i would want to share him, but when he is with you, i know that he is in good hands, that you will hold him close and love him. you fit with him in ways i could never. you fit with me in ways he could never, a dear friend i love with all my heart. 

after all, who else could understand better what it means to summon a god?
